Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.55,0:01:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们被她们威胁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.55,0:01:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 一种会让人做噩梦的魄力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.95,0:01:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你是这么脆弱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.45,0:01:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就不擅长动粗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.45,0:02:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审问到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.95,0:02:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行动将会被限制一段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.45,0:02:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要我核对一下战斗的纪录吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.85,0:02:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 不会有任何结果的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.05,0:02:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.35,0:02:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑事就加以隐瞒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.75,0:02:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公家机关的办事方法从来就没改变过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.45,0:02:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们曾经跟她们两个有些过节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.85,0:02:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她们两个以前经常是死对头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.45,0:02:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为老是互相干扰对方的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.75,0:02:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才在想难得跟她们进入了同一组织\N果然还是这种命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.95,0:03:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 那么Un-ou A-ou\N我命令你们消灭Eclair和Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十三话 冲突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很让人怀念呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.95,0:03:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好几十年没有看到这个星座了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.85,0:03:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时真嫉妒你的乐天性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.85,0:03:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在整个银河都是我们的敌人你明白吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.75,0:03:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 没人会想到我们会来这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.65,0:03:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惨的景象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说如此 但却没想到这么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.75,0:04:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 多么好的名字呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相转移反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亚空间传送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.25,0:04:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该要这么想才行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们怎么知道这个地方的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连Armbrust都不知道这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.15,0:04:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人这里有关系对吧？他们两个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salyut
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.75,0:04:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位逃亡者我好想见你们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.25,0:04:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Un-ou
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.25,0:05:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这的确是个绝佳的藏身之所\N但你们忘了我们的眼睛和耳朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.55,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你们还记得这个地方\N已经是几十年前的往事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记跟你们有关的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.05,0:05:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们多次把我们弄得很狼狈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.25,0:05:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是很想赶快忘记你们的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.65,0:05:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.65,0:05:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急亚空间跳跃失败\N相位转移航行装置发生异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.75,0:05:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早已习惯你们的伎俩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.95,0:05:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们太快了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.25,0:06:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的惯性控制系统看来比我们的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们冲着我们来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.75,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.65,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.65,0:06:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.25,0:07:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为两束光相碰 造成量子乱流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惯性控制系统超过负载了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.75,0:07:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我讨厌现在的制造商
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入防御模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.25,0:07:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.05,0:07:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是攻击我们的好机会呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎她们受到的损伤也很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 运气还站在我们这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wirbelwind 她怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.35,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠急救用的医疗纳米机械已经无法治疗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere 你没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能维持多久呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.55,0:08:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.75,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经活了很久了\N但最后的时刻到来的似乎太快了点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.55,0:08:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 帮我拿葡萄汁好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.15,0:08:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.25,0:08:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Dog Fight舰桥的3A控制板后面\N很久以前我藏了一瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.45,0:09:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们俩分享
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.75,0:09:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有多不容易死心 你应该最清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 我们要去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承诺之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.25,0:09:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你指的是那个…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.95,0:09:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为在那里有百万分之一的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.65,0:09:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百万分之一也不算是零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种性格真不好对付呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.05,0:10:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 你们俩不会衰老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.95,0:10:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼 什么也听不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.45,0:10:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.75,0:11:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多障碍的话 我的眼睛也没什么办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们也看穿我们的手法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那是这个殖民地的议事堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.25,0:11:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你搞的洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.35,0:11:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候本来可以赚很多钱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.85,0:11:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把前政权的政客抓来\N然后交给政变者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.35,0:11:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以有赚不完的赏金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.25,0:11:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明要抓来处决\N偏偏又要求活捉真让人费解的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她们又一次阻碍了我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.55,0:11:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让伤员先上 快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 我们是政变者的佣兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.25,0:12:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们是中央派来的治安管理官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.85,0:12:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我们是GOTT 而她们是逃亡者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.55,0:12:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世事真是有意思呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸行无常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.85,0:12:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世事的变化 只有上帝知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.75,0:12:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说话是不是越来越有禅机了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.85,0:12:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发现她们了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.15,0:12:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是她们残留的热量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.05,0:12:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.85,0:12:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们去外面了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.55,0:13:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩30分钟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果Lumiere出什么事 那我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.35,0:13:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况让我想起那时…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.45,0:13:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你受伤了而他在帮你的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你扶那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.65,0:13:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的医院就在附近 快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.95,0:13:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是数十年前的事了\N却还像是昨天的事一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说那么多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.75,0:14:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的话说不定能遵守约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便过了数十年 他或许还记得我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.35,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ganador
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.45,0:14:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Donner
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Donner Lumiere拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.85,0:15:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.35,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等这个时刻很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.85,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纠缠不休的男人会被讨厌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.95,0:15:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.95,0:15:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 就等一个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.15,0:15:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不马上接受治疗 Lumiere就会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.15,0:15:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很同情 但是没有这个必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.55,0:16:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接到的命令不是抓获 而是消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.05,0:16:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这里根本就没有能治疗她的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想试着找医生吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.35,0:16:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定好的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.65,0:16:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.05,0:16:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 你们俩不会衰老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.95,0:16:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我们一直在改变外形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.95,0:16:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我不能让你们留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.95,0:16:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑 只是玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.15,0:16:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不和我们一起离开这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场内战看来会持续很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.65,0:16:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该趁现在搬到更安全的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.65,0:16:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当这个殖民地再度恢复和平时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.55,0:16:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的恢复了 你们愿意再来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.45,0:16:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管到时候我可能已经是个老头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.55,0:16:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他保证过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.05,0:17:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们遇到困难 他随时会来帮我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.55,0:17:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他保证即便他死了 他也会留下能用的设备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.95,0:17:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 只要去他的医院 一定可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不想想那时到现在已经多少年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.95,0:17:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道这里后来发生了些什么吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.95,0:17:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定立刻就忘了那个承诺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.15,0:17:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算还记得 他也没有空去好好遵守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过普通生活的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.95,0:17:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说就像身边飘过的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.65,0:17:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你还相信那种口头的承诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.65,0:17:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能说你是个傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 你或许会这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.25,0:17:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴能认识你这么久 Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我会为你扫墓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.65,0:18:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-ou
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.25,0:18:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能为你做些什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像现在这样就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.65,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.65,0:19:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 多好的名字呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.55,0:19:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 Eclair Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.85,0:19:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.05,0:19:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道过了多少年\N你们才看到这个信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.35,0:19:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年后？50年后?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.15,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是更久之后的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.65,0:19:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这段影像的时间 是我们分离之后三年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.05,0:19:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战事不断恶化 到处在死人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道自己能活多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.65,0:20:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为了你们来的那一天\N我会留下这个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.85,0:20:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 就像我向你保证的那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.65,0:20:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到诊疗的时间了 再见Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.75,0:20:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Lumiere永远健康 和睦相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.55,0:20:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰兹 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能等到我们结束吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.75,0:20:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗？如此一来你们也是背叛者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOTT开始变得火药味十足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是我们改行的时候了
